About the Home:

In Mumbais favourite getaway destination, Alibaug, SaffronStays Nishta is a stunning 4-bedroom pet-friendly villa, overlooking an expanse of paddy fields. Adorned with an outdoor gazebo, private pool, manicured turf, a large terrace and balconies, its the perfect haven for a refreshing holiday with 2-3 families, hosting a corporate offsite or enjoying a reunion with friends.


What makes this home special?

The plenty of outdoor activities come with a promise of unending fun for you and your loved ones: while the little kids indulge in sports activities on the turf or in the kids pool, you can make the most of the tropical weather lounging in the large pool, walking barefoot on the lawn with your furry friend or unwinding in the gazebo.
The warm-toned earthy furnishings gorgeously complement the whitewashed walls running throughout the home and create a soothing atmosphere for you. 
The terrace on the second floor offers infinity views, perfect for hosting a sundowner and enjoying your evening revelries with your favourite tunes and a delicious BBQ!

A short flight of stairs leads you to a lobby, that opens to a small terrace. On the same level are 3 bedrooms (with ensuite bathrooms), 2 of which open to private balconies.
The second floor houses a large, open terrace with the finest views of the estate and lush green fields. The cool breeze and chirping birds will keep you company.


What can you do here: 

Enjoy a game of football or cricket with your gang on the fully-functional turf, or simply take a dip in the crystal waters of the pool to soak in the serenity.
Start your mornings with a hearty breakfast and a session of yoga on the lawn, binge on your favourite shows or plug in your favourite music in your rooms and wind down with your fam over a cosy bonfire.
